Waq_a_lat_ta_-ifatun min ahli alkit_a_bi_a_minoo bi*a*lla_th_ee onzila AAal_a_alla_th_eena_a_manoo wajha a*l*nnah_a_ri wa*o*kfuroo_a_khirahu laAAallahum yarjiAAoon*a*
Wal_a_tu\minoo ill_a_liman tabiAAa deenakum qul inna alhud_a_hud_a_All_a_hi an yu\t_a_a_h_adun mithla m_a_ooteetum aw yu_ha_jjookum AAinda rabbikum qul inna alfa_d_la biyadi All_a_hi yu\teehi man yash_a_o wa*A*ll_a_hu w_a_siAAun AAaleem*un*
