Wa-inna minhum lafareeqan yalwoona alsinatahum bi*a*lkit_a_bi lita_h_saboohu mina alkit_a_bi wam_a_huwa mina alkit_a_bi wayaqooloona huwa min AAindi All_a_hi wam_a_huwa min AAindi All_a_hi wayaqooloona AAal_a_All_a_hi alka_th_iba wahum yaAAlamoon*a*
M_a_k_a_na libasharin an yu\tiyahu All_a_hu alkit_a_ba wa*a*l_h_ukma wa*al*nnubuwwata thumma yaqoola li*l*nn_a_si koonoo AAib_a_dan lee min dooni All_a_hi wal_a_kin koonoo rabb_a_niyyeena bim_a_kuntum tuAAallimoona alkit_a_ba wabim_a_kuntum tadrusoon*a*
