Wa-i_th_akha_th_a All_a_hu meeth_a_qa a*l*nnabiyyeena lam_a__a_taytukum min kit_a_bin wa_h_ikmatin thumma j_a_akum rasoolun mu_s_addiqun lim_a_maAAakum latu\minunna bihi walatan_s_urunnahu q_a_la aaqrartum waakha_th_tum AAal_a__tha_likum i_s_ree q_a_loo aqrarn_a_q_a_la fa*i*shhadoo waan_a_maAAakum mina a*l*shsh_a_hideen*a*
